body:
Hex Casting & Iron's Spells 'n Spellbooks interop.

### Features

- New Iron's Spell: **Hex Grid** - opens hex casting grid;
- Being hit by **Counterspell** (vanilla Iron's spell) now closes and clears hex casting grid;
- New Hex Casting patterns:
  - Read Iron's spells from scrolls into iotas, and then cast them as yourself *or from other entities*! Supports all spells, including addons;
  - Conjure spellbook - a helper entity to cast Iron's spells from any position & direction;
  - Get Iron's spell cost, cooldown, cast time, cast type, level, max level;
  - Get spell which is being cast by entity; get time remaining until cast is finished;
  - Get spell cooldown, current & maximum mana of a player;
  - Downgrade iotified spell;
  - Reduce spell cooldown.
